  "id": "RAW_7158a3c2",
  "title": "MiniMax Music 2.0：让音乐创作属于每一个人",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5MTA3NzcxMQ==&mid=2247487060&idx=1&sn=f4eb7ad74cc237615c08a361a743cc81",
  "date": "2025-10-31 01:06:00",
  "author": "MiniMax 稀宇科技",
  "siteName": "MiniMax 稀宇科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd9b5f51&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmkSCPuQNUcjN2fjcREPib8K8ZNtmM3z4FH2PmZf8puicMl8ia1TvqXKDGuqtS16RUZO652fu6ib4PplQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，我们正式发布最新一代音乐模型——</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">MiniMax Music 2.0</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。这一版本中，模型对音乐的理解与表达实现了真正的跃升：无论是人声的细腻情绪，还是器乐的动态张力，都能被精准捕捉与还原。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它懂节奏，也懂情绪。在人声与器乐的交织中，它成为那个“会唱歌的制作人”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从此，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过音乐表达自己，不再是少数人的专利，而是每一个人都能获得的快乐。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">让灵感成为流动的乐句，Feel the rhythm, let the music belong to you.</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.人声灵动，驾驭不同唱法</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你不必接受声乐训练，也能用自己喜欢的声音，运用技法与风格，唱出心里的旋律。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在人声质感方面，Music 2.0 音色无限接近真实人声。此外，模型像一位老练的「唱将」，可驾驭多种唱法和情感风格；对乐句、节奏、呼吸恰到好处的处理，俨然拥有媲美真人的「唱商」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型支持对人声音色的精准控制，可以通过Prompt，保持核心音色一致的基础上，让同一声音切换不同唱法，实现一声千变，AI也可化身「百变唱将」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;NXKsdrvOuotGyOxBNmXcjTqEn2e&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;模型支持对人声音色的精准控制，可以通过Prompt，保持核心音色一致的基础上，让同一声音切换不同唱法，实现一声千变，AI也可化身「百变唱将」。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1z&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7449681373255811076&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;d2a1f99b-0a28-478e-959a-a355435820a9&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:25,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:71},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;doxcnmAhNKEEyQ9OeeHgoPbrBLd&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同一个女声，能够自如在Jump Blues、Rock、Electronic不同的风格间切换</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">除了能轻松驾驭流行、爵士、Blues、摇滚、民谣等常见唱法，模型还支持男女对唱、阿卡贝拉等风格。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;NXKsdrvOuotGyOxBNmXcjTqEn2e&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;除了能轻松驾驭流行、爵士、Blues、摇滚、民谣等常见唱法，模型还支持男女对唱、阿卡贝拉等风格。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1c&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7449681373255811076&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;488681e5-c953-4a10-8f85-e8c0b4736677&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:32,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:48},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;doxcn80GIYj2JYaTGdTI1OQ0Hid&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">男女声主唱不同的衔接效果，可以实现对话感、强弱变化的动态二重唱</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;NXKsdrvOuotGyOxBNmXcjTqEn2e&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;同一个女声，能够自如在Jump Blues、Rock、Electronic不同的风格间切换&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+19&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7449681373255811076&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;fa57f8f4-c67f-4af2-ac58-9155e283fece&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:true,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:30,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:45},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;doxcnoONihqgzOqpUs5PNihoMre&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">无伴奏，也能呈现丰富旋律</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">2.旋律抓耳，乐器精准控制</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你不必是编曲师，也能像编曲师那样，构建一首属于自己的完整乐章。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Music 2.0继承了上一代模型结构完整的优点，能够生成包含主歌、副歌、桥段等逻辑清晰、结构完整的歌曲。单首时长可达5min。此外新模型生成的旋律更容易记忆、能够迅速抓住耳朵。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hook部分旋律容易记忆，更具备真人创作时的旋律习惯</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在不同的风格表达中，模型可遵循精准的指令控制，对伴奏中的多种乐器进行独立控制与调整，实现层次丰富、律动自然的编曲。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;NXKsdrvOuotGyOxBNmXcjTqEn2e&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;在不同的风格表达中，模型可遵循精准的指令控制，对伴奏中的多种乐器进行独立控制与调整，实现层次丰富、律动自然的编曲。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1l&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7449681373255811076&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;4d36f198-903d-4f77-a716-40259e8281b4&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:74,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:57},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;doxcnwotBzpd95hnff7ZtEMHtag&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">萨克斯、长号、小号、爵士架子鼓、钢琴依次有序出现，宛如置身大师爵士现场</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">3.专业级音质体验</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">新模型也带来了全面的音质升级，无论是人声音轨质感，还是乐器空间感都更加增强，带给你沉浸式的听觉体验。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 32px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">复古disco舞池，充满活力的人声演唱和80年代经典乐器表现，带你回到那个翩翩起舞的黄金年代</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:17px;\">One More Thing</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们在测试 Music 2.0 时惊喜地发现，也可以通过 Prompt 精准描述人声情绪、声音场景等因素，生成影视级配乐独白。层层递进的情感与音乐铺陈，让人仿佛「听」到了画面的色彩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">惊喜之余，我们意识到，这得益于模型对于语义的准确理解，以及对人声表现力的精准控制——这正是模型语义理解与声学表达力的完美结合，让声音拥有多变的情感轮廓。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Music 2.0已经全面上线，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">欢迎开始创作，听见属于自己的惊喜：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">minimaxi.com/audio/music</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Intelligence with Everyone.</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100002934\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55546875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef7954fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGkCR4D4XPmK9WOI3vatCfyiazjxP2oTSSpmmdzQwrI0ibZlhDuAYgGmdoUw7c22962SfU35cBiaoTXow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "MiniMax 发布 Music 2.0，通过 AI 技术显著提升人声与器乐创作能力，旨在让每个人都能轻松进行专业级音乐创作。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "MiniMax 发布 Music 2.0，通过 AI 技术显著提升人声与器乐创作能力，旨在让每个人都能轻松进行专业级音乐创作。",
  "summary": "文章正式宣布 MiniMax 推出最新一代音乐模型 MiniMax Music 2.0，核心目标是降低音乐创作门槛，让普罗大众也能通过 AI 技术实现音乐表达。Music 2.0 在人声表现力方面取得突破，音色无限接近真实人声，能驾驭多种唱法和情感风格，并支持通过 Prompt 对人声音色进行精准控制，实现“一声千变”，包括男女对唱和阿卡贝拉。在器乐方面，模型继承了结构完整的优点，能生成长达 5 分钟、包含主歌、副歌、桥段等清晰结构的抓耳旋律，并支持对伴奏中多种乐器进行独立控制与调整。此外，Music 2.0 全面升级了音质，提供专业级的沉浸式听觉体验，并意外发现其具备生成影视级配乐独白的能力。文章强调 Music 2.0 将使音乐创作不再是少数人的专利，而是人人可享的快乐。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "MiniMax Music 2.0 显著提升人声表现力，支持多样唱法与情感控制",
      "explanation": "模型音色接近真实人声，可驾驭流行、爵士等多种风格，并能通过 Prompt 切换唱法，使非专业人士也能创作出富有情感的歌曲。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型具备结构化歌曲生成能力，可精准控制乐器编排",
      "explanation": "Music 2.0 能生成包含完整结构和抓耳旋律的歌曲，并支持对伴奏中各乐器进行独立指令控制，实现专业级编曲效果。"
    },
    {
      "point": "全面升级音质，提供沉浸式听觉体验，并拓展至影视配乐场景",
      "explanation": "新模型在人声和乐器音轨质感上均有提升，同时发现其语义理解与声学表达力结合，可用于生成影视级配乐独白。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "MiniMax Music 2.0：让音乐创作属于每一个人",
    "它懂节奏，也懂情绪。在人声与器乐的交织中，它成为那个“会唱歌的制作人”。",
